WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:01:05.700 --> 00:01:08.132
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

00:01:08.260 --> 00:01:11.172
=Episode 16=

00:01:16.519 --> 00:01:17.280
Empress Dowager,

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:19.319
Her Majesty's pulse shows no sign

00:01:20.200 --> 00:01:21.319
of pregnancy.

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:25.680
What's going on?

00:01:26.280 --> 00:01:26.840
Mother,

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:32.200
someone must have taken advantage
while the Xu generals and I were at war

00:01:32.200 --> 00:01:33.319
to slander Xu Yu

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:34.784
and bring down the Xu family.

00:01:35.319 --> 00:01:37.359
Once morale collapsed
on the battlefield,

00:01:38.079 --> 00:01:39.840
we would surely have lost the war.

00:01:40.159 --> 00:01:42.680
Whoever that person is,
their intentions are condemnable.

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:47.560
I nearly committed a grave error.

00:01:47.799 --> 00:01:48.319
Your Majesty,

00:01:48.760 --> 00:01:50.439
you must thoroughly investigate

00:01:50.560 --> 00:01:52.040
who orchestrated this plot.

00:01:52.040 --> 00:01:52.840
Don't worry, Mother.

00:01:53.239 --> 00:01:55.000
I've already ordered
a covert investigation.

00:01:57.079 --> 00:01:57.599
Mother,

00:01:58.560 --> 00:01:59.439
you misunderstood me.

00:01:59.879 --> 00:02:02.400
I dare to request an apology from you.

00:02:05.640 --> 00:02:06.680
I'm the Empress,

00:02:06.680 --> 00:02:07.480
the model for all.

00:02:08.199 --> 00:02:11.879
Any stain on my dignity affects
my authority over the harem

00:02:12.240 --> 00:02:14.360
and my ability to set
an example for our women.

00:02:16.680 --> 00:02:17.680
Therefore,

00:02:18.400 --> 00:02:19.520
I dare to ask for an apology

00:02:20.759 --> 00:02:21.800
from you.

00:02:28.840 --> 00:02:30.280
(Is Jinyun)

00:02:31.039 --> 00:02:32.280
(standing up for me?)

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:35.319
Mother,

00:02:36.319 --> 00:02:37.800
I also sincerely request

00:02:38.680 --> 00:02:39.879
you to clear her name.

00:02:48.919 --> 00:02:50.560
This was indeed

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:52.639
my fault for not trusting Xu Yu.

00:02:52.639 --> 00:02:54.680
I should apologize.

00:02:55.080 --> 00:02:56.240
Issue the command.

00:02:56.560 --> 00:02:57.599
From this day forward,

00:02:58.120 --> 00:02:59.759
anyone who spreads malicious gossip

00:03:00.039 --> 00:03:01.879
will face severe palace punishment.

00:03:02.120 --> 00:03:03.000
Thank you, Mother.

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:09.759
Marshal Xu Han, dispatched to the north,

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:11.240
resisted the barbarian tribes,

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:12.919
pushed back the Houyi troops,

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:14.240
and befriended Dada.

00:03:14.240 --> 00:03:15.360
His contributions are huge.

00:03:15.680 --> 00:03:18.919
The members of the Xu family
are all loyal and righteous,

00:03:18.919 --> 00:03:20.080
serving the empire

00:03:20.080 --> 00:03:21.360
and protecting His Majesty.

00:03:21.639 --> 00:03:23.960
Xu Han is hereby made
First-Class Marquis.

00:03:23.960 --> 00:03:25.599
The title shall be hereditary.

00:03:29.680 --> 00:03:31.280
Your Majesty, I am overwhelmed.

00:03:31.599 --> 00:03:32.439
My family and I

00:03:33.039 --> 00:03:34.039
are unworthy.

00:03:34.039 --> 00:03:35.800
Mr. Xu, please rise quickly.

00:03:36.560 --> 00:03:37.280
Thank you.

00:03:37.759 --> 00:03:38.400
Your Majesty,

00:03:38.719 --> 00:03:39.759
the late Emperor said,

00:03:39.759 --> 00:03:41.199
Chen requires civil governance.

00:03:41.400 --> 00:03:43.719
For military officers,
grant troops but not authority,

00:03:43.719 --> 00:03:45.120
grant authority but not titles,

00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:46.528
and grant titles but not troops.

00:03:46.599 --> 00:03:49.439
Your Majesty's bestowment
upon Marshal Xu is truly inappropriate.

00:03:49.759 --> 00:03:51.080
As the Emperor,

00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:52.240
I reward and punish fairly.

00:03:52.240 --> 00:03:53.159
What is inappropriate?

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:54.439
Your Majesty,

00:03:54.840 --> 00:03:58.400
a title of First-Class Marquis
can still gain acceptance,

00:03:58.919 --> 00:04:00.439
but making it hereditary

00:04:00.439 --> 00:04:01.960
contravenes ancestral regulations.

00:04:03.479 --> 00:04:06.039
If anyone can make Dada, Houyi,

00:04:06.280 --> 00:04:09.400
or any foreign tribe submit
a state letter and pledge allegiance,

00:04:09.680 --> 00:04:10.960
whether scholar or general,

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:13.152
I will grant the title
of First-Class Marquis.

00:04:19.456 --> 00:04:20.991
(From Dada's Huna)

00:04:26.639 --> 00:04:27.160
Your Majesty,

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:28.639
you're up so early?

00:04:29.759 --> 00:04:31.079
I was unaware

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:32.920
that while campaigning abroad,

00:04:33.199 --> 00:04:35.879
you still had energy to land me
in a romantic entanglement.

00:04:36.600 --> 00:04:39.199
The only men I interacted with
were my father and brother.

00:04:39.399 --> 00:04:40.360
Romantic entanglement?

00:04:41.240 --> 00:04:42.720
Queen of Dada, Huna,

00:04:43.040 --> 00:04:44.759
is coming to offer congratulations.

00:04:45.399 --> 00:04:48.160
Isn't friendly relations
between our two nations a great boon?

00:04:48.319 --> 00:04:49.319
A boon?

00:04:50.079 --> 00:04:50.959
So you mean

00:04:51.199 --> 00:04:54.519
you anticipated she would
send you a love letter?

00:04:58.079 --> 00:04:58.879
This letter

00:04:59.600 --> 00:05:03.639
begins with the words,
"My longing for you flows like a river."

00:05:08.639 --> 00:05:09.680
That's impossible!

00:05:09.680 --> 00:05:11.360
How could this love letter be for me?

00:05:11.360 --> 00:05:12.319
I'm a woman.

00:05:13.639 --> 00:05:14.139
Oh, right!

00:05:14.240 --> 00:05:15.680
I was using Your Majesty's body.

00:05:15.800 --> 00:05:16.300
You...

00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:19.160
Are you suggesting

00:05:19.519 --> 00:05:20.639
that I take a concubine?

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:22.800
You're quite generous, aren't you?

00:05:23.839 --> 00:05:24.480
Your Majesty.

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:25.800
That's not what I meant.

00:05:25.920 --> 00:05:26.839
As you know,

00:05:27.360 --> 00:05:28.399
in my heart,

00:05:29.040 --> 00:05:29.759
there is only...

00:05:43.120 --> 00:05:44.160
Only what?

00:05:48.759 --> 00:05:49.759
Only...

00:06:09.240 --> 00:06:09.920
You're here.

00:06:09.920 --> 00:06:10.420
Sit.

00:06:11.759 --> 00:06:12.319
Sit.

00:06:12.439 --> 00:06:12.939
Sit.

00:06:31.959 --> 00:06:32.519
How's it?

00:06:32.959 --> 00:06:33.519
Your Majesty,

00:06:33.680 --> 00:06:35.439
I've studied the sacred Soul Silk

00:06:35.800 --> 00:06:37.079
sent by Queen Huna all night

00:06:37.519 --> 00:06:40.720
and finally conceived
a method to swap souls back.

00:06:41.319 --> 00:06:41.920
But...

00:06:42.839 --> 00:06:44.439
it requires cooperation from you two.

00:06:45.680 --> 00:06:46.560
How do we cooperate?

00:06:47.560 --> 00:06:49.240
During the moment of thunder,

00:06:49.800 --> 00:06:50.959
Your Majesties,

00:06:51.199 --> 00:06:52.199
as yin and yang,

00:06:53.040 --> 00:06:54.240
must make intimate contact.

00:06:55.120 --> 00:06:56.519
Intimate?

00:06:56.959 --> 00:06:57.959
Contact?

00:06:58.600 --> 00:07:00.519
Like what I saw when I entered just now.

00:07:01.040 --> 00:07:01.879
That's easy, right?

00:07:06.439 --> 00:07:06.939
Right.

00:07:08.360 --> 00:07:09.600
Before the thunder arrives,

00:07:09.959 --> 00:07:11.199
Your Majesties,

00:07:11.839 --> 00:07:12.680
please practice more.

00:07:15.240 --> 00:07:16.079
Practice more.

00:07:25.760 --> 00:07:28.704
(Fengyi Palace)

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:52.439
We...

00:07:53.439 --> 00:07:54.560
We just start like this?

00:07:55.120 --> 00:07:56.160
Then what should we do?

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:57.560
How about we eat first?

00:07:58.199 --> 00:07:58.720
Fine.

00:07:59.160 --> 00:08:00.040
Eat first.

00:08:09.920 --> 00:08:12.319
Why are we drinking so late at night?

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:15.040
This is medicinal wine
I brought back from Dada.

00:08:15.439 --> 00:08:17.920
It nourishes yin and strengthens yang.

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:22.560
My body doesn't need strengthening.

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:26.500
You...

00:08:29.139 --> 00:08:32.440
You were poisoned with a fake pregnancy.
You still need recuperation.

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:34.639
You haven't taken today's medicine.

00:08:35.120 --> 00:08:35.639
This...

00:08:35.960 --> 00:08:37.879
This medicine is terribly bitter.

00:08:38.279 --> 00:08:41.639
You can't refuse to take it
just because it's bitter.

00:08:42.320 --> 00:08:44.639
If it weren't for your health,

00:08:44.639 --> 00:08:46.360
why would I take such bitter medicine?

00:08:46.679 --> 00:08:48.720
Wasn't it because of you
that I was poisoned

00:08:48.720 --> 00:08:50.039
and now, I have to take

00:08:50.039 --> 00:08:51.080
a bitter tonic to recover?

00:08:51.799 --> 00:08:52.879
Xu Yu.

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:54.000
Your Majesty.

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:54.639
Take it.

00:09:02.559 --> 00:09:03.320
It's time

00:09:04.840 --> 00:09:06.360
to take your medicine.

00:09:07.919 --> 00:09:08.960
I'll do it myself.

00:09:09.919 --> 00:09:11.480
Come on.

00:09:17.440 --> 00:09:17.960
What's wrong?

00:09:21.159 --> 00:09:23.960
T-This medicine
is too bitter to sip slowly.

00:09:23.960 --> 00:09:25.480
Let it cool a bit more.

00:09:25.480 --> 00:09:26.940
I'll take it all at a time, okay?

00:09:28.799 --> 00:09:31.039
How bitter can it be?

00:09:38.679 --> 00:09:39.840
Silly.

00:09:45.559 --> 00:09:46.519
How am I silly?

00:09:46.720 --> 00:09:49.240
If you weren't silly,
would you have tested it for me?

00:09:55.879 --> 00:09:56.399
Xu Yu!

00:09:56.679 --> 00:09:57.279
Xu Yu!

00:10:04.960 --> 00:10:05.519
Mother.

00:10:05.840 --> 00:10:06.679
Don't worry.

00:10:07.200 --> 00:10:08.519
His Majesty is blessed.

00:10:08.759 --> 00:10:09.840
He will be fine.

00:10:15.879 --> 00:10:17.200
How is His Majesty?

00:10:21.399 --> 00:10:22.120
Empress Dowager,

00:10:22.440 --> 00:10:24.679
His Majesty is poisoned.

00:10:25.039 --> 00:10:27.519
But the symptoms differ
from common poisons.

00:10:27.960 --> 00:10:31.440
I can't find an antidote now.

00:10:32.240 --> 00:10:33.799
Is His Majesty's life in danger?

00:10:34.879 --> 00:10:35.799
Not for now.

00:10:36.159 --> 00:10:36.960
But His Majesty

00:10:37.799 --> 00:10:39.960
is unlikely to wake up soon.

00:10:41.519 --> 00:10:42.039
Mother.

00:10:42.879 --> 00:10:43.559
My child!

00:10:44.200 --> 00:10:45.120
Empress Dowager,

00:10:45.360 --> 00:10:46.559
Grand Master Zhang is here.

00:10:47.600 --> 00:10:48.720
Grand Master Zhang.

00:10:49.240 --> 00:10:49.759
Let him in.

00:10:50.440 --> 00:10:51.000
Mother,

00:10:51.320 --> 00:10:53.039
why has he suddenly come to the palace?

00:10:53.600 --> 00:10:55.720
When His Majesty campaigned in Dada,

00:10:56.159 --> 00:10:57.879
I was always uneasy,

00:10:58.200 --> 00:11:00.240
so I frequently summoned
Grand Master Zhang.

00:11:02.399 --> 00:11:04.320
Empress Dowager.

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:06.600
You've come at just the right time.

00:11:06.919 --> 00:11:08.120
Come examine His Majesty.

00:11:08.440 --> 00:11:09.440
He's unconscious.

00:11:10.080 --> 00:11:11.799
I'm terribly anxious!

00:11:12.159 --> 00:11:13.360
Don't worry, Empress Dowager.

00:11:18.039 --> 00:11:20.559
A few nights ago, I observed
the celestial phenomena.

00:11:20.559 --> 00:11:22.320
The Emperor Star appeared dim.

00:11:22.320 --> 00:11:23.879
Evil spirits have entered His Majesty.

00:11:24.240 --> 00:11:26.000
If you trust me,

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:29.759
I'll perform a ritual tomorrow
at noon to expel the evil spirits.

00:11:29.759 --> 00:11:32.120
I believe His Majesty will awaken.

00:11:32.759 --> 00:11:33.259
Good.

00:11:33.600 --> 00:11:35.120
Do it tomorrow at noon.

00:11:35.240 --> 00:11:36.360
Just let us know

00:11:36.360 --> 00:11:37.280
if you need anything.

00:11:50.360 --> 00:11:51.320
What is he doing?

00:11:51.759 --> 00:11:54.159
Before the ritual starts,
no one may speak.

00:11:54.320 --> 00:11:55.360
I will assist.

00:11:56.759 --> 00:11:58.399
His Majesty's safety is paramount.

00:11:58.840 --> 00:12:00.480
He cannot be left alone with you.

00:12:01.039 --> 00:12:02.000
I am the Empress.

00:12:02.799 --> 00:12:04.120
I should be by his side.

00:12:45.840 --> 00:12:46.559
What is that?

00:12:46.720 --> 00:12:48.240
Please remain calm, Empress Dowager.

00:12:48.440 --> 00:12:51.000
To save His Majesty,
we must use fire therapy.

00:12:51.399 --> 00:12:52.960
If the process is interrupted rashly,

00:12:52.960 --> 00:12:54.200
His Majesty will be in danger.

00:13:15.480 --> 00:13:16.039
Your Majesty!

00:13:16.360 --> 00:13:16.960
Your Majesty!

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:31.399
What kind of trick is this?

00:13:32.200 --> 00:13:33.360
You performed it just now.

00:13:33.840 --> 00:13:35.240
Why is this one different?

00:13:35.759 --> 00:13:37.759
I know you can fight,

00:13:38.559 --> 00:13:40.919
so I have mixed

00:13:41.159 --> 00:13:42.240
a little knockout incense

00:13:42.799 --> 00:13:43.799
into the flames.

00:13:44.080 --> 00:13:45.200
Who exactly are you?

00:13:48.519 --> 00:13:50.000
Do you find

00:13:50.240 --> 00:13:51.120
my voice

00:13:51.879 --> 00:13:53.399
familiar?

00:13:55.799 --> 00:13:56.960
Marquis of Zhenbei!

00:14:08.879 --> 00:14:09.379
Jinming!

00:14:11.240 --> 00:14:11.879
What's wrong?

00:14:12.279 --> 00:14:13.480
Go to save His Majesty!

00:14:14.320 --> 00:14:14.820
Alright!

00:14:31.919 --> 00:14:32.480
No!

00:14:32.480 --> 00:14:33.080
Xu Yu!

00:14:33.600 --> 00:14:34.320
You're awake!

00:14:35.240 --> 00:14:36.799
I'll push you out of the fire later.

00:14:37.159 --> 00:14:39.679
We cannot both die here.

00:14:40.039 --> 00:14:40.720
No!

00:14:40.960 --> 00:14:41.759
Xu Yu.

00:14:42.480 --> 00:14:43.519
In our next life,

00:14:44.879 --> 00:14:45.759
wait for me.

00:14:46.279 --> 00:14:47.000
No!

00:14:47.879 --> 00:14:49.320
If we cannot live together,

00:14:50.159 --> 00:14:51.720
we shall die together.

00:15:10.340 --> 00:15:15.524
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

00:15:16.260 --> 00:15:20.823
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

00:15:22.148 --> 00:15:27.563
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

00:15:28.132 --> 00:15:32.676
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

00:15:33.316 --> 00:15:38.580
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

00:15:38.948 --> 00:15:44.625
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

00:15:44.964 --> 00:15:46.980
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

00:15:47.172 --> 00:15:50.916
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

00:15:51.492 --> 00:15:56.164
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

00:15:56.708 --> 00:15:58.468
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

00:15:58.788 --> 00:16:02.404
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

00:16:02.651 --> 00:16:08.178
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪